<item>
 <title>How China&#039;s 13th Five-Year Plan Addresses Energy and the Environment</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/how-chinas-13th-five-year-plan-addresses-energy-and-environment</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Beijing%20skyline%20blue.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;197&quot; height=&quot;120&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default&quot;/&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-author&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    Deborah Seligsohn and Angel Hsu        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This post &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafile.com/reporting-opinion/environment/how-chinas-13th-five-year-plan-addresses-energy-and-environment&quot;&gt;originally appeared&lt;/a&gt; on ChinaFile.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For the first time ever, a senior Chinese leader announced in his &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/03/05/world/asia/china-li-keqiang-work-report-full-text.html?_r=0&quot;&gt;work report&lt;/a&gt; to the National People’s Congress—his most important formal speech of the year—that environmental violators and those who fail to report such violations will be “severely punished.” Premier Li Keqiang reported that China had succeeded in meeting or exceeding the previous Five-Year Plan’s environmental goals. The draft 13th Five-Year Plan, released March 5 and scheduled to be passed (likely without amendment) in the coming days, builds on that success, requiring greater reductions in the emissions of many pollutants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/how-chinas-13th-five-year-plan-addresses-energy-and-environment&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;read more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
 <category domain="http://www.chinafaqs.org/category/issue-areas/chinafaqs-theme-why-china-acting-clean-energy">ChinaFAQs Theme: Why China is Acting on Clean Energy</category>
